<!-- HOW WE DO IT -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tighter mb-4">How We Do It</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary max-w-3xl mb-10">An epoxy grout upgrade isn't a patch job. We remove all your old cement grout and replace it with professional-grade epoxy for a result that lasts decades.</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">1</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Assess Your Shower</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">We inspect every grout line, check for loose tiles, and look for signs of water damage or <a href="<?php echo esc_url( home_url( '/services/shower-leak-repair-sydney/' ) ); ?>" class="text-primary underline font-medium">shower leaks</a>. We photograph the current condition and confirm epoxy grout is the right solution for your tiles and layout.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">2</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Remove All Old Grout</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Using oscillating multi-tools fitted with diamond blades, we remove every bit of old cement grout back to the tile edge. Epoxy grout cannot go over old grout &mdash; complete removal is essential for proper adhesion and a lasting result.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">3</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Clean the Joints</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">All joints are vacuumed and wiped clean to remove dust, debris, and any mould or residue from behind the old grout. Clean joints are critical &mdash; epoxy grout bonds to the tile edge, so the surface must be completely free of contamination.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">4</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Apply Epoxy Grout</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Professional-grade two-part epoxy grout is mixed on-site and pressed firmly into every joint. Epoxy grout has a shorter working time than cement, so we work methodically in sections to ensure consistent coverage and a clean finish.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">5</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Finish &amp; Clean Excess</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">Excess epoxy is cleaned from tile faces before it cures. This step requires experience &mdash; epoxy grout sets hard and is extremely difficult to remove once cured. We leave every tile face clean and every grout line uniform.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold mb-4">6</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-sm mb-2">Replace All Silicone</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-secondary leading-relaxed">All old silicone at floor-wall junctions and internal corners is stripped out and replaced with premium wet-area silicone rated for long-term mould resistance. This completes the watertight seal across your entire shower.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

